    "scope_check": "strategist-scope per roledef. F0 is a new deliverable not in the original v1 roadmap or addendum; surfaced by engineer's Phase E handoff observation. Director-implicit-ratification per no-clarifying-questions mode 2026-05-11. F1-F5 unchanged from original Phase F roadmap.",
    "phase_e_disposition": "Complete; SHA-256 round-trip verified production thingalog-organization.opencatalog; opencatalog substrate works; openbraid is implementation #1 of orgdef SCHEMA v1.0.0. C7 closed by E5 absorption.",
    "f0_rationale": "Without artifact-position claimability, Phase E's URL-as-instruction is half-functional (read boot payload OK, but cannot become the role). Self-host (Phase G) lands a half-functional system. Panel UX (F1-F5) without F0 mostly improves legacy paths. F0 is the natural completion of Phase E's artifact path.",
